title: Empire Cast - Original Soundtrack From Season 1 [FLAC 16 Bit]
description:
All of these songs are from the singles & albums that were released during the airing of Season 1. I reorganized, edited, and sorted everything in chronological order (from when they appear in the show). I even edited some of the songs to replicate the ones in the show. Enjoy
